\chapter{测试步骤}
\label{index:id2}
\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
CREATE TABLE wd
(
    bm integer NOT NULL,
    sheng integer,
    shi integer,
    szd integer,
    psfw text,
    bpsfw text,
    mc character varying(100),
    CONSTRAINT wd\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (bm)
);

CREATE TABLE psfw
(
    id integer NOT NULL DEFAULT nextval('areas\_id\_seq'::regclass),
    bm integer,
    dz character varying(80),
    szd integer,
    pslb integer, -- 1全送排除 2全不送排除 3送 4不送
    CONSTRAINT areas\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id)
)；
CREATE INDEX psfw\_dz\_idx
    ON psfw
    USING btree
    (dz COLLATE pg\_catalog."default");


CREATE TABLE psfw\_lu
(
    id integer NOT NULL DEFAULT nextval('roadnums\_id\_seq'::regclass),
    psfw\_id integer,
    xiao integer,
    da integer,
    dsh integer, -- 0 不区分单双号 1 单号 2双号
    CONSTRAINT roadnums\_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id)
)
CREATE INDEX psfw\_lu\_xiao\_da\_idx
    ON psfw\_lu
    USING btree
    (xiao, da);
\end{Verbatim}

psfw表存储szd-区县 dz-地址 pslb 类别 dzidx测试索引列

psfw\_lu 表为 psfw子表，当psfw表中dz为路且派送或者不派送范围不为全路段时，在

psfw\_lu表中记录门牌号码，xiao起始号码 da终止号码 ，dsh，标记奇偶数号码

用imdata1.py把mysql gsjj表导入到pgsqldb中

用addip.py处理pgsqldb表，数据进psfw表

然后，增加一个tsquery列，做全文索引查询用：

\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
\PYG{k}{ALTER} \PYG{k}{TABLE} \PYG{n}{psfw} \PYG{k}{ADD} \PYG{k}{COLUMN} \PYG{n}{dzidx} \PYG{n}{tsquery}\PYG{p}{;}
\PYG{k}{CREATE} \PYG{k}{INDEX} \PYG{n}{psfw\PYGZus{}dzidx\PYGZus{}idx}
    \PYG{k}{ON} \PYG{n}{psfw}
    \PYG{k}{USING} \PYG{n}{gist}
    \PYG{p}{(}\PYG{n}{dzidx}\PYG{p}{)}\PYG{p}{;}
\PYG{k}{update} \PYG{n}{psfw} \PYG{k}{set} \PYG{n}{dzidx}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n}{to\PYGZus{}tsquery}\PYG{p}{(}\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}chinesecfg\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{p}{,}\PYG{n}{dz}\PYG{p}{)}\PYG{p}{;}
\end{Verbatim}

由于测试数据不规范，只进行bm=213300 szd=320481的公司进行测试，从ldb表中处理路、小区数据进入psfw psfw\_lu 表，然后 用ldb表中数据进行测试

用procdata1.py 处理ldb表中bm=213300数据进入psfw .

更新213300派件网点所在地为999169，测试用（由于导入数据不准）
\begin{quote}

update psfw set szd =999169 where bm=213300
\end{quote}

建立联合索引

\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
\PYG{k}{CREATE} \PYG{k}{INDEX} \PYG{n}{psfw\PYGZus{}szd\PYGZus{}dzidx\PYGZus{}idx}
\PYG{k}{ON} \PYG{n}{psfw}
\PYG{k}{USING} \PYG{n}{btree}
\PYG{p}{(}\PYG{n}{szd}\PYG{p}{,} \PYG{n}{dzidx}\PYG{p}{)}\PYG{p}{;}
\end{Verbatim}

查询语句，耗时10ms级

\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
\PYG{k}{select} \PYG{o}{*} \PYG{k}{from} \PYG{n}{psfw} \PYG{k}{where} \PYG{n}{szd}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+m+mi}{999169}  \PYG{k}{and} \PYG{n}{to\PYGZus{}tsvector}\PYG{p}{(}\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}chinesecfg\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{p}{,}\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}骆驼街道贵驷里洞桥村洞桥路60号\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{p}{)} \PYG{o}{@}\PYG{o}{@} \PYG{n}{dzidx}
\end{Verbatim}

查询门牌号 60

\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
\PYG{k}{select} \PYG{o}{*} \PYG{k}{from} \PYG{n}{psfw} \PYG{n}{p} \PYG{k}{inner} \PYG{k}{join} \PYG{n}{psfw\PYGZus{}lu} \PYG{n}{l}
\PYG{k}{on} \PYG{n}{p}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{id}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n}{l}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{psfw\PYGZus{}id}
\PYG{k}{where} \PYG{n}{p}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{szd}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+m+mi}{999169}  \PYG{k}{and} \PYG{n}{to\PYGZus{}tsvector}\PYG{p}{(}\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}chinesecfg\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{p}{,}\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}骆驼街道贵驷里洞桥村洞桥路\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{p}{)} \PYG{o}{@}\PYG{o}{@} \PYG{n}{p}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{dzidx}
\PYG{k}{and} \PYG{p}{(}\PYG{l+m+mi}{60} \PYG{k}{between} \PYG{n}{l}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{xiao} \PYG{k}{and} \PYG{n}{l}\PYG{p}{.}\PYG{n}{da}\PYG{p}{)}
\end{Verbatim}
